      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col text-left text-gray-300">
        <h3 class="text-sm">Regulations:</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 text-xs font-thin">
          <a href="/regulations/marketing">Marketing</a>
          <a href="/regulations/rodo">RODO</a>
